text:
Alexander Sebastian Léonce, Baron von der Wenge, Count Lambsdorff (born 5 November 1966), commonly known as Alexander, Count Lambsdorff () is a German politician of the Free Democratic Party of Germany. He was a Member of the Bundestag (MP) and Member of the European Parliament (MEP) from Germany.
Lambsdorff tested positive for COVID-19 in March 2020.
